    "description": "凭借一个既无情又令人上瘾的移动系统，你的游戏技能将受到终极考验！进入杰夫这个有着人类双腿的乌龟寻找父亲的荒诞世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/72e03ab3d34ec23c4bc7672306061cda.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7837f38d5a9cfb0e13f453e3483206d4.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7837f38d5a9cfb0e13f453e3483206d4.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7837f38d5a9cfb0e13f453e3483206d4.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>困难的移动</strong>：速度是成功的关键，移动得越快，跳得越远。根据速度来把握跳跃时机，落到你需要去的地方，或者不跳，随你便！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7209e6669e303de82a0775aae8e904b6.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/cd73767abe292c9395620e96eec952e8.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/cd73767abe292c9395620e96eec952e8.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/cd73767abe292c9395620e96eec952e8.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>充满挑战的世界</strong>：由于杰夫是一只小乌龟，即使是最小的障碍对他来说也是巨大的挑战！带领他穿越危险的沙地、苔藓、雪地，甚至太空！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/d3d39dd15e45845447fff4e337333f1b.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/ae59cc596e0f680cce8bacc931e2db17.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/ae59cc596e0f680cce8bacc931e2db17.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/ae59cc596e0f680cce8bacc931e2db17.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>独特的主角</strong>：引导我们那只拥有巨大人类大腿的古怪乌龟杰夫，穿越一系列令人费解的障碍和令人捧腹的时刻。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/5c2a92903a9ad98e66c457226f1526ab.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/dc4fcdacde7003e36137f81e35a37416.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/dc4fcdacde7003e36137f81e35a37416.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/dc4fcdacde7003e36137f81e35a37416.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>搞笑时刻</strong>：花费数小时尝试并失败于同一个跳跃！我保证，有人会觉得听到你对着电脑屏幕尖叫很有趣！</li></ul><br>准备好在引导杰夫的旅程中愤怒、大笑和哭泣，这个游戏难以玩却让人无法放下。<br><br>你准备好迎接挑战了吗？",
